<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="draw-near-closer">draw near / closer</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>接近；靠近：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Christmas is drawing near.
圣诞节就要来了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>With the Spring Festival drawing near, people will hold all varieties of activities.
随着春节的临近，人们将举办丰富多彩的庆祝活动。</p><footer>2009 山东书面表达</footer></div></div>